{
  "stem": "7832.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in the ghetto until they finished building the railroad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while we were there, of course everybody was working really hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- there were tortures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were-- there were a lot of-- a lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of people starved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot of people had no medication.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was very little that we got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Packages were coming in from the outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they said that was our ration, but I-- I-- we-- we thought that the Jews that were still in the city were-- were doing that, they were sending in.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For one, I know my father had a cousin that lived all his life in Munkacs, and he owned a store.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was called the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That means the yellow store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they sold materials like for clothing and I don't know what you call that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You know for clothing, and for different things-- all kind of materials.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we knew that they were still home, they weren't taken to the ghetto yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my father's cousin that had the resort in Polana, he also lived in Munkacs in the hotel, and they were still home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so they were sending us food from the outside into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then when the railroad got finished, when they finished the railroad coming into the ghetto, nobody was allowed to come in, or we weren't getting any communications from the outside.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In fact, they were bringing people in from the city into the ghetto and boarding the-- the railroad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And again, we were told that we-- now we're going to Tokaj and we were going to make wine in Tokaj until the war is over.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
